		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=33064"><span id=>azkurat</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br>7 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=azkurat&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>West Commonlands would be a decent spot to move to after Neriak.&nbsp;&nbsp;Although with the new orc camps you might be able to bypass West Commonlands.  The bandit camps make for a decent exp grind at lower levels.  Once you hit 14 lvl or so I'd say Go Go Go to Paludal Caverns.  Stay there until around 26th, which will come fast.<br><br>If there are enough peeps to get groups, then Crystal Caverns can be a nice spot for low to mid 30's.  I went from 33 to 34 in one night of 5 hours of play.<br><br>Also watch for the 'hot spots'.  They give exp bonus' and will be well populated, so pulls might be hard, but you'll be able to find groups.  Try to stick to indoor dungeons.  You get an exp bonus for these.<br><br>General hits for SK<br>Learn to be an outstanding puller.  Learn how to work Mob Pathing, How to FD on time, and learn when to Take a Death instead of training your group and causing a wipe out.  Taking a Death instead of causing a wipe out will earn you a great deal of respect and get you a good rep.  Good rep = lots of peeps wanting you in their groups.<br><br>Learn how to handle Agro.  Keeping and loosing it.  Also learn how to work well with Chanters.  Learn how to get your targets from them.  Learn how to break mezz without ping-ponging the mob onto the chanter. (taunt, debuff, taunt, debuff, taunt, Dot)  Mezz will break on the DoT and you'll have the mob really pissed at you.<br></p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr>